00:30:46,100 --> 00:30:48,200
 To bring glory to Hong Kong.

551
00:30:48,200 --> 00:30:54,400
 Imagine if we as Christians

552
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:55,700
 are as committed

553
00:30:55,700 --> 00:31:00,900
 to guarding Christ and his truth

554
00:31:00,900 --> 00:31:04,000
 as much as Edgar is willing

555
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:06,900
 to devote himself to a sport of fencing.

556
00:31:06,900 --> 00:31:11,400
 He dedicated his life,

557
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:14,000
 started from a young age to fencing,

558
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:16,100
 and eventually he worked so hard,

559
00:31:16,100 --> 00:31:18,400
 even though he was the underdog,

560
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:20,900
 he won the gold medal.

561
00:31:20,900 --> 00:31:25,000
 Are we willing to dedicate our life

562
00:31:25,000 --> 00:31:27,700
 to guard the gospel truth,

563
00:31:27,700 --> 00:31:29,400
 to stand for his truth,

564
00:31:29,400 --> 00:31:31,700
 to use our gifts,

565
00:31:31,700 --> 00:31:33,300
 dedicate our life,

566
00:31:33,300 --> 00:31:40,100
 protect what has been entrusted to us?

567
00:31:40,100 --> 00:31:41,700
 Are we willing to do that?

568
00:31:41,700 --> 00:31:47,500
 And then eventually, we will also be champions.

569
00:31:47,500 --> 00:31:51,000
 Champions for the Lord.

570
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:55,400
 To receive the crown of glory

571
00:31:57,700 --> 00:32:00,300
 that Jesus has promised

572
00:32:00,300 --> 00:32:02,900
 and Paul later talks about

573
00:32:02,900 --> 00:32:06,000
 in the rest of the chapters.

574
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:10,000
 Let us take some time to respond

575
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:12,500
 as the band comes up.

576
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:17,000
 Are we willing to stand on guard?

577
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:21,000
 Let's take a moment to just think about

578
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:24,300
 what has God entrusted you with?

579
00:32:27,100 --> 00:32:28,600
 Your gifts.

580
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:34,400
 Your ministry.

581
00:32:34,400 --> 00:32:37,000
 The people around you.

582
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:42,300
 The truth, the Bible, gospel truth.

583
00:32:42,300 --> 00:32:46,100
 God has entrusted you with these things.

584
00:32:46,100 --> 00:32:51,300
 Are you willing to guard these things?

585
00:32:51,300 --> 00:32:55,400
 To use these things, fan into flame?

586
00:32:56,400 --> 00:32:58,900
 The gifts that you have been given.

587
00:32:58,900 --> 00:33:02,100
 Surrender these things.

588
00:33:02,100 --> 00:33:06,100
 Surrender your emotions, your fears to the Lord.

589
00:33:06,100 --> 00:33:09,100
 Are you willing?

590
00:33:09,100 --> 00:33:20,200
 Let's just take a moment to pray and seek the Lord.

591
00:33:20,200 --> 00:33:22,700
 What has he entrusted us?

592
00:33:23,500 --> 00:33:26,000
 (soft music)

593
00:33:26,000 --> 00:33:38,700
 Heavenly Father, we thank you for this message.

594
00:33:38,700 --> 00:33:43,100
 Paul's charge to Timothy,

595
00:33:43,100 --> 00:33:45,600
 to guard his spiritual gifts.

596
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:47,000
 Not be fearful.

